# Node.js Toolchain

Pinned versions (single source: `package.json` → `engines`):

| Tool | Version | Also defined in |
|------|---------|-----------------|
| Node.js | **20.18.3** | `.nvmrc`, `.node-version` |
| npm | **10.8.2** | `packageManager` |

When bumping Node/npm, update **all** of the above plus CI uses `node-version-file: .nvmrc`.

Local setup: `nvm install && nvm use` or `fnm use`.

Do not suggest Node 22+ or npm 11+ unless the user explicitly upgrades the pinned toolchain.
